{"by":"sminchev","id":47764777,"kids":[47764947],"parent":47764215,"text":"Robots are everywhere. Especially in the factories. \nI think making things automatic is good, all those stupid jobs, moving all day something from one place to another, manually is pure waste of human energy. If this energy is redirected to education, and more meaningful work, those people will be much more valuable for their community and the world. If robots are used in that direction, they can do a lot of good things, and there will be no ethical lines to cross.<p>Helping people enhance is a good thing!","time":1776169841,"type":"comment"}